data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. You will fall in LOVE with this 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a Den or Bonus Room, located on a corner lot in Port Charlotte. The Kitchen is lovely featuring Leathered Granite Countertops and Tile Backsplash, upgraded Fixtures & Appliances. Go, Green, this home comes complete with a 9.4kwh whole home Solar System & New Roof in 2022 with 50-year shingles. Newer Septic System in 2017, High Impact Hurricane Rated Windows. If you are looking for a Workshop? Come check out this anchored-down Weather King 12×20 Dutch style shed with 2 lofts,  which features full-service electricity with 50 amp wiring for a generator or RV. 12,000 BTU mini split system built in 2019. All utilities are underground. The home is located within 2.5 miles of the all-new Sun Seeker Resort, Shopping, Golf, and the Punta Gorda Airport. This home is a must-see. With too many upgrades to mention here ask your agent for the upgrade list. This home has so many updates, ask your agent to see the attached list. These types of homes don't last!
